Package pda.view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApercuView
    The ApercuView is the page displaying a modified image
    We chose this image on the GalleryView.
    Chargement
    Chargement is the page displaying there is a current loading
    ChoosePhotoView
    The ChoosePhotoView is the page displaying the images of the chosen directory
    It displays thoses images in 2 or 3 columns
    EditPhotoView
    The EditPhotoView is the most important page of the application
    It display a chosen photo and allow to do effects on it.
    FilterImage
    A Filter to only load images on the application
    GalleryView
    The ApercuView is the page displaying a modified image
    We chose this image on the GalleryView.
    HelloView
    The simplest application in the PDA.
    ImagePanel
    Is a panel with a backgroup image
    LaunchView
    The LaunchView application that starts all others.
    NewViewport  
    ParamView
    The ParamView is the parameters pages.
    PdaView
    The base class of PDA simulator.
    PhotoBoostView
    The PhotoBoostView is the first page of the Photoboost's interface
    This page displays the parameters menus and the access to the galleries.
